Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:18.10,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are the best!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:20.85,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Nobody can ever stop us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:22.48,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because we are the best!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:23.73,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, touch the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:24.98,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}ビルディング伸びる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:28.19,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}狭い空見上げ Close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:31.70,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The next moment 広がる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:34.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}踏み出せば I’ll have a new experience
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.33,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We go back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:37.66,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we are who we are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.46,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}見失わず 前へ Go on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:41.83,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Count on you, flyin’ up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:46.17,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anywhere, we can handle everything so well
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:47.63,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}常に冷静に Manage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:49.30,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}平凡な檻からFly away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:50.34,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just like a business
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.84,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}世界を見極め Negotiate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.59,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To live is continuously to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:58.18,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Until I die, no end in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.93,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I believe in our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.73,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}繋がってる　確かなパス
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:05.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your power still flows into me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.36,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感じてる　大切なものをこの肩に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.86,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}きみとならFly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:15.32,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I decided to become a sage of the stars, oh like you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.20,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh oh (Push forward!! Pu- Push forward!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.25,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh oh (Flyin’ high!! Fl- Flyin’ high!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:24.37,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}止まる事ない二つのタイムライン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.96,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}変えていく　さあ二人でRight now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:28.46,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:29.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:30.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on! Go on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:35.76,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}何処までもきみとFly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:15.35,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}無論發生什麼事 都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:16.89,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因為我們是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:18.10,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我們是最好的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:20.85,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}沒有人能阻　{擋}我們
