Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:29.71,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能與　做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:29.71,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(625,12)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:30.80,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}繼續前進！繼續前進!!
